\sqrt{b} = \frac{|a|}{\sqrt{n}}
x_1=x_2 = \cdots = x_n
(x_1 + x_2 + \cdots + x_n) \leq \sqrt{n} \sqrt{x_1^2 + x_2^2 + \cdots + x_n^2}
a^2 \leq nb
(n,a,b) = (20,200,2000)
a^2 = 200^2 = 40000 = 20 \times 2000 = nb
